    "Software comprises the computer code enabling user interaction within the Metaverse.",
    "Depending on the information system and metadata availability, the generated virtual worlds can significantly vary.",
    "They can range from an initial model with a singular, simple and generic vision to a more advanced model that incorporates a simulation engine capable of analyzing the data established by the programmer and fostering immersive interactions within the Metaverse (Sébastien et al. 2009).",
    "Achieving the highest level of immersion requires metadata from all non-human participants (NHP) within the Metaverse through three approaches: textual description, visual representation, and formalized rules that define the behaviors of NHP present in the Metaverse.",
